ğŸ’¡ GOLDEN RULE:
   "Business logic should not depend on infrastructure.
    Infrastructure should depend on business logic."

ğŸ¯ KEEP IT SIMPLE:
   Start with the domain, add application layer, 
   then build infrastructure around it.

